A Mac OS X Screen saver where you can watch your seconds (and minutes and hours) slowly drain away. Depressing and fun, at the same time!

Download: "DrainSaver-1.0.zip":http://cloud.github.com/downloads/fdb/drainsaver/DrainSaver-1.0.zip.

This wraps the work of the following reddit post:

http://www.reddit.com/r/programming/comments/8zxgy/i_love_clocks_and_javascript_and_canvas_so_i_made/

See the original version in a browser:

http://www.blahbleh.com/clock4.php

Source code by blahbleh at blahbleh dot com.

Mac OS X port by frederik at pandora dot be.
